<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Delivered</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #FFF8E7;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
      border-top: 4px solid #D4AF37;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #D4AF37;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .success-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4AF37 0%, #F4D03F 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .delivery-icon {
      font-size: 64px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .order-info {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8E7 0%, #FAF0E6 100%);
      border: 1px solid #F4D03F;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .order-number {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #D4AF37;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .delivered-time {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .message-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8E7 0%, #FAF0E6 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid #D4AF37;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #D4AF37;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #F5F5DC;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">üçΩÔ∏è SureSpot</div>
      <h1 class="title">Order Delivered!</h1>
      <div class="success-badge">‚úì Successfully Delivered</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="delivery-icon">üì¶‚ú®</div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>Great news! Your order has been successfully delivered.</p>
      
      <div class="order-info">
        <div class="order-number">Order #{{orderNumber}}</div>
        <div class="delivered-time">Delivered on {{deliveredAt}}</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="message-box">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #D4AF37;">
          üéâ Enjoy your meal!
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
          We hope you love your order. If you have any feedback, we'd love to hear from you!
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for choosing SureSpot. We look forward to serving you again!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} SureSpot. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
